EXTRACTION
Britney and Silk are dispatched to the Austrian Alps to rescue a famous mathematician and his family from a radical terrorist organization that is holding them hostage. But the duo is still learning how to work together and any mistakes could hold deadly consequences. Can the new teammates come together to free the family in time, or will the majestic white slopes run red with blood?
